    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dents, and there are signs of wear on the interior including some fading and light scuffs on the upholstery. The engine starts and runs, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term. All major systems are functional, but this vehicle is not without its flaws and should be inspected before purchase.",
